As I understand it, yes.  Early Traveller had a number of jokes of
this sort inserted in.  As I recall, the official line was that the
Aslan were named by the early Solomani explorers who were the "first"
to contact one of the Aslan starfaring clans.  The meaning of the
name "Aslan" is lost in obscurity as far as Imperial citizens are
concerned.  :)  

