    'topic' => 'Alternate Weapon Paradigms',
    'body' => 'I am curious if anyone has developed weapons from an alternate culture or race 
that follow a different paradigm than 20th century Earth.  Obviously, there 
are only so many ways to design a weapon that propels a high-velocity object 
over a distance to it\'s target, but what if a culture never developed chemical 
propellants?  What would their weapon paradigm be?  

I thought perhaps a culture might have a curved weapon launcher of some sort 
(think jai alai).  Perhaps if they did eventually create explosives of some 
sort they might still propel the explosive down a curved barrel.

The idea here is to have an entire history of weapons development that is 
totally "alien" in design and appearance, but is niether primitive or too 
extremely advanced.

