Some figures will remain on the tips of everyone\'s tongue. Some names will
be forever lost. Name 3 Egyptian Pharoahs. Now, which one had his
burial crypt found intact, which one is a major brand of condoms and
you must have stayed awake in history to remember a third name. Now,
who built the Great Pyramid?  That\'s tougher, but you could do it.
Which pharoah imposed the greatest tax burder on his people? I doubt
anyone will get that one (without making it up or having a PhD).
(Note my use of the Egyptian metaphor as I don\'t know a thing about
